  <data key="d9">"Java class account located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Defines methods get address1, get address2, get banner name, get city, get country, get email, get favourite category id, get first name, get language preference, get last name, get password, get phone, get state, get status, get username, get zip, is banner option, is list option, set address1, set address2, set banner name, set banner option, set city, set country, set email, set favourite category id, set first name, set language preference, set last name, set list option, set password, set phone, set state, set status, set username, set zip."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Account class is responsible for managing user account information, providing getter and setter methods for attributes such as name, address, email, password, and preferences. It also tracks account status and banner options."</data>
