<node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.service.CatalogService">
  <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.service.CatalogService"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CatalogService"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">""</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class catalog service located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.service. Uses related classes category, category mapper, item, item mapper, product, product mapper. Defines methods catalog service, get category, get category list, get item, get item list by product, get product, get product list by category, is item in stock, search product list."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CatalogService class is responsible for managing product catalogs, providing operations to retrieve and search product information, such as categories, items, and products. It offers methods to access and manipulate product data, including listing, retrieving, and checking stock availability."</data>
