  <data key="d9">"Java class item located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Uses related classes product. Defines methods get attribute1, get attribute2, get attribute3, get attribute4, get attribute5, get item id, get list price, get product, get quantity, get status, get supplier id, get unit cost, set attribute1, set attribute2, set attribute3, set attribute4, set attribute5, set item id, set list price, set product, set quantity, set status, set supplier id, set unit cost, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Item class is responsible for managing item attributes and product information, providing getter and setter methods for various attributes such as quantity, list price, and unit cost, as well as a reference to the associated Product. It also tracks the item's status and supplier ID."</data>
