  <data key="d9">"Java class cart item located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Uses related classes item. Defines methods calculate total, get item, get quantity, get total, increment quantity, is in stock, set in stock, set item, set quantity."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CartItem class is responsible for managing a single item in a shopping cart, providing operations to calculate the total cost, retrieve and update item details, and manage stock quantities. It maintains a reference to an Item object and tracks its quantity and stock status."</data>
