  <data key="d9">"Java class category located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Defines methods get category id, get description, get name, set category id, set description, set name, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Category class is responsible for managing category data, providing methods to retrieve and update its name, description, and ID. It also offers a string representation of the category."</data>
