  <data key="d9">"Java class account service located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.service. Uses related classes account, account mapper. Defines methods account service, get account, insert account, update account."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The AccountService class is responsible for managing account data, providing operations to retrieve, insert, and update account information. It interacts with the Account and AccountMapper classes to perform these operations."</data>
