<node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper.AccountMapper">
  <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper.AccountMapper"</data>
  <data key="d1">"AccountMapper"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">""</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class account mapper located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper. Uses related classes account. Defines methods get account by username, get account by username and password, insert account, insert profile, insert signon, update account, update profile, update signon."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The AccountMapper class is responsible for managing Account data, providing operations to retrieve, insert, and update account information, as well as related signon and profile data. It offers methods to interact with Account objects in a database-like context."</data>
