<node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain.LineItem">
  <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain.LineItem"</data>
  <data key="d1">"LineItem"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">""</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class line item located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Uses related classes cart item, item. Defines methods calculate total, get item, get item id, get line number, get order id, get quantity, get total, get unit price, line item, set item, set item id, set line number, set order id, set quantity, set unit price."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The LineItem class is responsible for managing a single line item in an order, providing operations to access and modify its properties such as quantity, unit price, and total cost. It appears to be a data container for a line item in a shopping cart or order."</data>
