  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class order located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Uses related classes account, cart, cart item, line item. Defines methods add line item, get bill address1, get bill address2, get bill city, get bill country, get bill state, get bill to first name, get bill to last name, get bill zip, get card type, get courier, get credit card, get expiry date, get line items, get locale, get order date, get order id, get ship address1, get ship address2, get ship city, get ship country, get ship state, get ship to first name, get ship to last name, get ship zip, get status, get total price, get username, init order, set bill address1, set bill address2, set bill city, set bill country, set bill state, set bill to first name, set bill to last name, set bill zip, set card type, set courier, set credit card, set expiry date, set line items, set locale, set order date, set order id, set ship address1, set ship address2, set ship city, set ship country, set ship state, set ship to first name, set ship to last name, set ship zip, set status, set total price, set username."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Order class is responsible for managing the details of a customer's order, including billing and shipping information, order status, and associated line items. It provides getter and setter methods for these details, allowing for initialization and modification of the order."</data>
