  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class account action bean located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions. Inherits from abstract action bean. Uses related classes account, account service, catalog service, product. Defines methods clear, edit account, edit account form, get account, get categories, get languages, get my list, get password, get username, is authenticated, new account, new account form, set my list, set password, set username, signoff, signon, signon form."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The AccountActionBean class is responsible for managing user account actions, providing methods for authentication, account editing, and password management. It interacts with related classes such as Account, AccountService, and CatalogService to perform these actions."</data>
