  <data key="d9">"Java class order service located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.service. Uses related classes item, item mapper, line item mapper, order, order mapper, sequence, sequence mapper. Defines methods get next id, get order, get orders by username, insert order, order service."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The OrderService class is responsible for managing orders, providing operations to retrieve and insert orders, as well as related items and sequences. It offers methods to get orders by username, retrieve a specific order, and generate the next order ID."</data>
