  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class order mapper located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper. Uses related classes order. Defines methods get order, get orders by username, insert order, insert order status."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The OrderMapper class is responsible for managing orders, providing operations to retrieve, insert, and update order data. It offers methods to access and manipulate orders, including retrieving orders by username and inserting new orders and order statuses."</data>
